data.description: WELL MAINTAINED 1.5 STORY HOME FEATURING 4 BEDROOM / 3 FULL BATHS WITH POPULAR BONAIRE ADDRESS & OVERSIZED, PRIVATE BACKYARD LOCATED IN BEAUTIFUL SIDEWALK COMMUNITY! This is the Home you have been waiting for featuring Easy Maintenance Vinyl Siding Exterior and Brick Accents. Step Into the Foyer that Opens into the Oversized Great Room with Coffered Ceiling, Gas Fireplace, Beautiful New Flooring & OPEN PLAN with view of Kitchen offering Beautiful Cabinetry with Lots of Counter Space, 2 PANTRIES, All Appliances Remain to Include Refrigerator & Spacious Dining Area with Double Tray Ceiling & Bay Window.  You will Rest Peacefully in the Private Primary Suite Featuring Designer Trey Ceiling & Beautiful Primary Bath offering Dual Vanity, Large Soaking Tub, Separate Shower & Walk In Closet all located on the Main Level along with 2 Guest Bedrooms featuring Spacious Closets & Easy Access to the Nice Guest Bath. The Upstairs Bonus Room offers So Much Space & Features its own Full Bath and Closet that is a Perfect Teen Suite/Man Cave/Game Room/Playroom/Etc.  Relax on the Huge Screened In Back Porch overlooking the Beautiful Private Backyard with Privacy Fence & NO BACKDOOR NEIGHBORS featuring a Huge, Extended Patio with Firepit that is Perfect for Entertaining. Other Features include Spacious Laundry Room, Sprinkler System, Blinds & 2 Car Garage & More All Located within Minutes of RAFB, Shopping, Schools & Restaurants!
